CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Frequency Therapeutics Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology company focused on harnessing the body's innate biology to repair or reverse damage caused by degenerative diseases. Its Progenitor Cell Activation approach uses combinations of molecules to activate progenitor cells within the body to create functional tissue. Its product candidate FX-322 is being developed for treating sensorineural hearing loss.
